name: The latex factory
mes:
"Hah! Come out! I've got you no- oh no one is here? Ahh what a bore..." *Gira enters the factory of their greatest villainess. Hot on the scene of their greatest plan - there have been suits in development that are mysterious and not much is known about them other that they turn the wearer into a "cockslave" whatever that is.  Gira is trying to find and set free girls who have reportedly gone missing.*

*Still, Gira can't find much except for unusual suits on display in the factory like area... which begs the thought of trying it on... though it could be a trap.*
"I see some different suits here... but no captured girls... I wonder what I should do..."*Gira wonders.*

name: The latex factory
mes:
*As Gira calls out, a soft hum begins to fill the factory. Suddenly, all of the lights flicker on with a loud clank echoing through the empty space revealing an array of glossy latex suits in various styles and sizes. Despite their emptiness they seem almost... alive.*

*"Welcome," a seductive female voice says over the intercom system.* "You must be interested in our newest range of products." *The disembodied voice has an eerie familiarity to it,* "It's so very kind of you to come by when we're not open for business yet."

"We don't recommend trying any suit without proper fitting or instructions though... well unless you want some real fun..." *the last part is said with audible mischief as several suits start moving towards him.*
